<definitions typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI">

  <process id="twittertest" name="2-step Twitter Test Process" isExecutable="true">
    <startEvent id="startevent1" name="Start"/>
    <endEvent id="endevent1" name="End"/>
    <userTask id="form1" name="Form Task 1" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_test1_form"/>
    <serviceTask id="fact1" name="Fact Task 1" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_test1_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow1" sourceRef="startevent1" targetRef="form2"/>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow3" sourceRef="form1" targetRef="endevent1"/>
    <boundaryEvent id="boundarymessage1" name="Message" attachedToRef="form1" cancelActivity="false">

    <serviceTask id="fact2" name="Fact Task 2" activiti:class="plugins.facts">

      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow id="flow14" sourceRef="form2" targetRef="servicetask3"/>

flow.name: io.point.Twitter_provider
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL">
  <process isExecutable="true" name="io.point.Twitter_provider" id="io.point.Twitter_provider">
    <startEvent name="Start" id="startevent1"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_List_Objs" name="List Objects" id="GETobjs">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_List_Recs" name="List Records" id="GETobjtypes">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Read_Obj_toFields" name="Read Record" id="GETobj">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">
          <activiti:expression>${objId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Update_Obj_fromFields" name="Update Record" id="PUTobj">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">
          <activiti:expression>${objId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Read_Obj_toFields" name="Read Record Again" id="GETobj2">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="objKey">
          <activiti:expression>${objId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>{$accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.fact_components.api_Twitter_Create_Obj_fromFields" name="Create Record" id="POSTobj">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="objType">
          <activiti:expression>${objTypeId}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="data">
          <activiti:expression>${data}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerKeyVal">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerKeyVal}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="consumerSecret">
          <activiti:expression>${consumerSecret}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTok">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTok}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="accessTokSec">
          <activiti:expression>${accessTokSec}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <exclusiveGateway default="default" name="Exclusive Gateway" id="exclusivegateway1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="exclusivegateway1" sourceRef="startevent1" id="flow1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="GETobj2" sourceRef="PUTobj" id="flow10"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="GETobjs" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="GETOBJS" id="flow12">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GETOBJS"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="GETobjtypes" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="GETRECS" id="flow13">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GETRECS"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="GETobj" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="GET" id="flow14">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "GET"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="PUTobj" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="PUT" id="flow15">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method == "PUT" || apidata_method == "PATCH"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="POSTobj" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="POST" id="flow20">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${apidata_method=="POST"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="GETobj2" id="flow16"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="GETobj" id="flow17"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="GETobjtypes" id="flow18"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="GETobjs" id="flow19"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="POSTobj" id="flow21"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" name="Unsupported" id="default"/>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_default_view" name="Default" id="usertask1"/>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_tweet_view" name="Tweet" id="usertask2"/>
